====HOW TO USE:=====
1. Open Lol Surprise Dolls wallpaper HD
2. Choose your favorite picture
3. Tap the "Set as wallpaper" button to apply
4. Your wallpaper has been changed


==== FTag Category:====



====FEATURES:====
1. Much Cool Lol Surprise Dolls HD Wallpapers
